++ Trivial Feedback

TF is an AvailableOption where [Feedback] will [AlwaysFeedback] regardless of how trivial it is. TF is possible with DirectedLogic.

    * [Open]
    * Status
    * [Update]
    * [Protocols] and [Network] communication
    * Discovery

++Examples
    * when a cookie is saved, the user knows about it
    * DHCP: toast table with two sided arrows pointing to chosen dhcp server out of the possibilities 